Erasing flash memory of ESP32 and ESP8266 board with ESPTOOL
============================================================

From command line:
------------------
py -3.9 -m pip install esptool

py -3.9 -m esptool

py -3.9 -m esptool --chip ESP8266 --port COM<port number> erase_flash

Example:
py -3.9 -m esptool --chip ESP8266 --port COM3 erase_flash

/The port number is checked in the Arduino IDE: Tools -> Port.../
